  <brief_title>Prospective Data Collection of Elderly Patients With DLBCL Receiving at the Time of Diagnosis VGM</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Data Collection of Elderly Patients (≥ 65 Years) With Diffuse Large B-cell Lymphoma (DLBCL) Receiving at the Time of Diagnosis Multidimensional Geriatric Assessment (VGM)</official_title>
